.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-6-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, november, september, january
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, colombian, indonesian, turkish
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, guinea-pig, pony, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, ship, skateboard
 1. the owner of the goldfish is not the turkish##6
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
 3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 4. the turkish is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
 6. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the turkish is in an odd position##4
 9. the chinese is on the far right##1
10. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
11. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
12. the indonesian is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
13. the person driving the bike is not the chinese##6
14. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | september   | november      | january   | may |
| Nationality   | indonesian | colombian  | turkish | chinese     |
| Pet           | rabbit     | guinea-pig | pony    | goldfish    |
| Transport     | skateboard | car        | bike    | ship        |

